comments: really like the class, its not always exactly clear why we are learning certain things but i think i am starting to understand why he shows us such a range of things. i like the tasks we get and the meetings that we have each week to talk about our ideas and the feedback

He always shows me loads of places where I can look for inspiration for my work and he seems to know about a lot of things to help with my essays.
he is always interested in hearing about my projects and gives good tips and advice
